title: Burning Love (season 1) (HDTV)
description:
"Burning Love" is a scripted comedy series which is a spoof of the television shows "The Bachelor", "The Bachelorette" and "Bachelor Pad".

It's created by Erica Oyama, and features actors and actresses from a long range of comedy series, including "Childrens Hospital", "NTSF:SD:SUV::" and many others.

These are the scene rips of season 1 of the TV series (not the webisodes), broadcast on E! early in 2013.
